      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 1
      - text: 但那裡如今已成了怪物盤據的可怕廢墟。
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n除了想搜刮武器的盜賊外，沒人會接近。"
  RetMSG_Bado_01_1:
    attributes: Npc_Road_001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: 位於東之岩山背面的古代
      - control:
          kind: set_colour
          colour: blue
