      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n聽說裡頭藏著傳說級的武器，\n而且數量還不少……"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: "\n聽好了！"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: long
      - text: 那裡非常危險，所以絕對不能去找喔！
